<article id="article-<%= @article.id %>" class="h-entry">
  <header class='span2 offset1'>
    <div class='meta'>
      <p class='text-right'>
        <img src='<%= File.join(this_blog.base_url, "images/theme/frederic-de-villamil-circle.jpg") %>' style='margin-top: 10px' /><br />
        <small><span class='bold'><%= @article.user.nickname %></span><br />
          <time>le <%= display_date(@article.published_at) %></time>
        </small>
      </p>
      <hr />
      <p class='text-right'>
        <small>
          <%= tag_links(@article, "<span class='bold'>Dans</span><br />") unless @article.tags.empty? %>
        </small>
      </p>
      <hr />
      <p class='text-right'>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/share?url=<%= URI.encode(@article.permalink_url) %>&amp;text=<%= URI.escape(@article.title) %>&amp;via=fdevillamil"><img src="/images/theme/twitter_icon_bw.png" alt="Partagez sur Twitter"></a>
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=<%= URI.encode(@article.permalink_url) %>&amp;t=<%= URI.escape(@article.title) %>"><img src="/images/theme/facebook_icon_bw.png" alt="Partagez sur Facebook"></a>
        <a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=<%= URI.encode(@article.permalink_url) %>&amp;hl=fr"><img src="/images/theme/googleplus_icon_bw.png" alt="Partagez sur Google Plus"></a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=<%= URI.encode(@article.permalink_url) %>&amp;title=<%= URI.escape(@article.title) %>"><img src="/images/theme/linkedin_icon_bw.png" alt="Partagez sur Linkedin Plus"></a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>  

  <div class='span8'>
    <h1 class='page-header p-name'><%= link_to_permalink(@article,@article.title) %></h1>

    <%= @article.html(:body) %>
    <%= @article.html(:extended) %>

    <footer>
      <div class='well'>
        <img src='/images/theme/frederic-de-villamil-square.jpg' alt="Frédéric de Villamil" class='alignleft' /> 
        Une information, une correction ou un complément à ajouter en privé ? Envoyez moi un petit mail à <a href='mailto:frederic@t37.net'>frederic@t37.net</a>. N'hésitez pas aussi à faire un tour sur <a href='http://twitter.com/fdevillamil' rel='external nofollow'>Twitter</a>, <a href="https://plus.google.com/118260479267451543665/posts" rel="external nofollow">Google+</a> ou encore <a href='http://www.facebook.com/RayonUx' rel='external nofollow'>Facebook</a> pour d'autres news.
      </div>

      <%= render_similar_posts @article %>  
    </footer>
</article>
